                   </div>
                </div>
                <div className="flex-1">
                  <h3 className="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">N8N Webhook Configuration</h3>
                  <p className="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">Enter the webhook URL from your N8N workflow to generate real FedEx labels.</p>

